    "description": "未能陪伴子女身边的父亲必须赶在入住岛潮酒店最后一晚前救回自己深陷邪教的女儿。在该真人互动悬疑游戏中，玩家将尽全力解救 Eleanor Malone，会在调查的过程中遭遇一系列奇异事件，而玩家所做出的每个决定都会影响故事后续发展。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/d0b6ca68ac3a2ddf097b61cc82b1dd82.poster.avif?t=1727964070\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/d0b6ca68ac3a2ddf097b61cc82b1dd82.webm?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/d0b6ca68ac3a2ddf097b61cc82b1dd82.mp4?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这间酒店每三年经营三晚。每当营业时，酒店会迎来形形色色人物，他们各自掩饰着自己的心灵创伤，解密将所有人联系在一起的线索。他们在寻找生命的意义。但今晚，这个神秘组织必须决定是否需要打破教规，把一名少女交给神出鬼没的创教人—Aniston 博士。Aniston 博士向众人献祭少女能让他们实现目标。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/b25db0cb8175b38d241bd2823681f5e0.poster.avif?t=1727964070\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/b25db0cb8175b38d241bd2823681f5e0.webm?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/b25db0cb8175b38d241bd2823681f5e0.mp4?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你将如何渗透进这家酒店？你会一路掩人耳目，混入邪教组织吗？你能否发现隐世传说、支线任务以及对应的特有结局，又或是在无情剧情解谜任务中经受挫败？触发分支剧情，用尽各种方法拯救你素未谋面的女儿。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/8da98f0d4210e44205905d59318d031b.poster.avif?t=1727964070\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/8da98f0d4210e44205905d59318d031b.webm?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/8da98f0d4210e44205905d59318d031b.mp4?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>主要玩法 <br>•\t根据个人决策引发剧情的真人互动游戏 <br>•\t包含 7 个主要结局和 14 种不同的游戏结果 <br>•\t设有特色结局的支线任务 <br>•\t实时性格和邪教追踪系统 <br>•\t游戏内章节选择菜单——获得菜单后即可使用 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/556b0c7bae737a71a1d8990d769214b5.poster.avif?t=1727964070\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/556b0c7bae737a71a1d8990d769214b5.webm?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/556b0c7bae737a71a1d8990d769214b5.mp4?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>剧情玩法 <br>•\t一个有着丰厚历史底蕴和繁琐教规的独特邪教组织 <br>•\t解密并发现封锁的小路 <br>•\t触发隐藏结局的神秘笔记 <br>•\t隐世传说和彩蛋等你来发现 <br>•\t扩展对话选项可让你从不同角度了解同一人物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/c5542b4ac090710a1fc8cf5adcb9d214.poster.avif?t=1727964070\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/c5542b4ac090710a1fc8cf5adcb9d214.webm?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000090/extras/c5542b4ac090710a1fc8cf5adcb9d214.mp4?t=1727964070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
